with the Western people.

00:12:47.920 --> 00:12:51.240
Now with the Eastern people I&nbsp;
will tell them something else,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:55.320
but with you I have to tell you something else.

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:59.120
You know that very well that&nbsp;
we have to tackle problems&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:02.600
