and also know how to save others.

00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:53.560
We know how to cure others.

00:13:53.560 --> 00:13:58.600
We know all about medicines.
We can cure cancer.

00:13:58.600 --> 00:14:02.640
We can cure ourselves, we can cure others.

00:14:02.640 --> 00:14:11.280
And all this comes to us so easily.
Apart from that we understand the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:11.280 --> 00:14:18.560
relationship between science and Sahaj Yog,&nbsp;
between economics and Sahaj Yog, between&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:18.560 --> 00:14:27.040
politics and Sahaj Yog, between physics and&nbsp;
Sahaj Yog, and between so many other branches&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:33.440
of knowledge with Sahaj Yog, because they&nbsp;
are also part and parcel of human beings.&nbsp;

00:14:33.440 --> 00:14:38.480
We start understanding psychology&nbsp;
through Sahaj Yog in a new way.

00:14:38.480 --> 00:14:42.040
We start understanding all&nbsp;
the scriptures of the world,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:42.040 --> 00:14:47.440
because everything is enlightened,&nbsp;
and we understand Sahaj Yog.

00:14:47.440 --> 00:14:55.000
But we do not become fully&nbsp;
that, which we have to be.

00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:58.320
We do not fully manifest our Spirit.

00:14:58.320 --> 00:15:16.080
If so, we would be completely in joy.
The reason for that is very simple,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:20.920
that in the beginning when we start feeling the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:20.920 --> 00:15:29.080
vibrations, when you get the first&nbsp;
Realization, it’s in a very big way.

00:15:29.080 --> 00:15:31.480
You enjoy that experience.

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:38.760
Then Kundalini starts going to other places to&nbsp;
supply, for example, to your brain to begin with.

00:15:38.760 --> 00:15:44.600
Because you have used your brain too much,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:49.840
and still you are using your&nbsp;
brain to know about Sahaj Yoga.

00:15:49.840 --> 00:15:53.560
I think in the beginning when&nbsp;
we had started our work here,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:53.560 --> 00:15:57.200
people used to ask Me questions after questions.

00:15:57.200 --> 00:16:02.880
I mean, all sensible questions, I mean,&nbsp;
all about the knowledge of Sahaja Yoga.

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:09.520
It’s all concerning the knowledge&nbsp;
of Sahaj Yoga, nothing outside,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:09.520 --> 00:16:14.800
because what is outside Sahaja Yoga I don’t know.

00:16:14.800 --> 00:16:24.880
But still it was only&nbsp;
questioning about it, not being.

00:16:24.880 --> 00:16:29.280
So, how do we grow in Sahaj Yoga?

00:16:29.280 --> 00:16:33.440
When we have such a thinking capacity.

00:16:33.440 --> 00:16:36.200
First you jump into thoughtless awareness.

00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:38.960
Means a thought that rises&nbsp;
within you and falls off,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:38.960 --> 00:16:42.880
and another thought that rises within&nbsp;
you and falls off – the space in-between&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:42.880 --> 00:16:48.960
those two thoughts, that is the one we&nbsp;
achieve through our Kundalini awakening.

00:16:48.960 --> 00:16:51.600
We have to establish that space.

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:56.360
Now what is that space?

00:16:56.360 --> 00:17:04.520
That’s the mouth of our entry into&nbsp;
the processes of the Divine power.

00:17:04.520 --> 00:17:07.120
Say for example, this is the mouth of this mike.

00:17:07.120 --> 00:17:13.800
If I say something here or here it won’t work out.
It will only work out when I say something here.

00:17:13.800 --> 00:17:21.320
In the same way, if you have a problem,&nbsp;
to begin with, a Sahaja Yogi will try to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:21.320 --> 00:17:28.360
solve it the way he has been solving it before&nbsp;
– like he’ll rationalize it, he’ll analyze it.

00:17:28.360 --> 00:17:32.880
He’ll sit with other Sahaja Yogis,&nbsp;
sit down and analyze Sahaja Yoga also.

00:17:32.880 --> 00:17:37.360
Is a very common pastime with&nbsp;
some of the Sahaja Yogis.

00:17:37.360 --> 00:17:39.280
There’s nothing to analyze in Sahaja Yoga.

00:17:39.280 --> 00:17:43.800
It is the synthesis.

00:17:43.800 --> 00:17:52.080
So what we have to do is to feel it more within&nbsp;
us and establish that thoughtless awareness.

00:17:52.080 --> 00:18:03.760
Any problem you have – I’ll give you an example, a&nbsp;
very simple example of Regis having, coming to Me.

00:18:03.760 --> 00:18:12.480
He had his thesis to be put for&nbsp;
examination and he was fed up.

00:18:12.480 --> 00:18:17.760
He couldn’t, he didn’t even have patience&nbsp;
to put in a proper bound and all that.

00:18:17.760 --> 00:18:20.920
And he came to Me and he said, “Mother&nbsp;
what to do with this?” I said, “All right,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:18:20.920 --> 00:18:26.600
you bring your thesis to Me.” I took&nbsp;
the thesis in My hand, that’s all.

00:18:26.600 --> 00:18:31.320
He said, “Aren’t You going to read it?” I said,&nbsp;
“No, there’s no need to read it.” I just closed&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:18:31.320 --> 00:18:39.120
My eyes, and gave it back to him, I said, “You&nbsp;
put it for examination”, and third day he was PhD.

00:18:39.120 --> 00:18:40.240
Now what did I do?

00:18:40.240 --> 00:18:41.920
No magic, nothing.

00:18:41.920 --> 00:18:42.800
It’s no magic.

00:18:42.800 --> 00:18:45.640
It’s so practical.

00:18:45.640 --> 00:18:47.880
God has His own powers.

00:18:47.880 --> 00:18:49.520
He has His own machinery.

00:18:49.520 --> 00:18:52.360
He has His own government, He has everything.

00:18:52.360 --> 00:18:58.720
Which is dynamic! You can’t imagine&nbsp;
how many dimensions He can work it out.

00:18:59.680 --> 00:19:03.760
Just you have to put it in&nbsp;
the mouth of that machinery.

00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:08.480
If you can do it you get the results easily.

00:19:08.480 --> 00:19:18.560
Only one thing God cannot do, that is&nbsp;
to make you sensible, to make you wise,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:19:18.560 --> 00:19:22.960
that’s one thing that’s your own&nbsp;
lookout, that’s in your own choice.

00:19:22.960 --> 00:19:27.080
Because you are guided by your ego.

00:19:27.080 --> 00:19:28.720
You are identified with your ego.

00:19:29.760 --> 00:19:38.240
And anything I say may upset&nbsp;
you, or may appeal to you.

00:19:38.240 --> 00:19:46.520
God knows how you are going to react.
But only way you can grow is to be in&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:19:46.520 --> 00:19:51.920
the center to see, not to&nbsp;
go to extremes of anything.

00:19:51.920 --> 00:19:54.360
To be in the center.

00:19:54.360 --> 00:19:58.640
Even listening to Me try to be in the center.

00:20:00.280 --> 00:20:04.680
But human beings are funny as I told&nbsp;
you, you see, they must go to extremes.

00:20:04.680 --> 00:20:08.040
You give them any job they&nbsp;
must go to the extremes.

00:20:08.040 --> 00:20:12.160
Anything you give them they cannot keep to&nbsp;
the centre, they can never keep the balance.

00:20:12.160 --> 00:20:16.360
Now see, this one, if it could not&nbsp;
be balanced, how can I speak on that?

00:20:16.360 --> 00:20:21.640
I mean, in day-to-day life we never sit&nbsp;
without a balance on a chair, do we?

00:20:21.640 --> 00:20:24.760
Do we sit on one side all the time?

00:20:24.760 --> 00:20:28.640
