one side – declined like that?

00:20:29.880 --> 00:20:34.360
Do we do anything that is under&nbsp;
imbalance – say for example,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:20:34.360 --> 00:20:37.600
these lights, how they are well balanced.

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:44.120
It has to be in balance everything, but in our&nbsp;
behavior towards God we are very much imbalanced.

00:20:44.120 --> 00:20:48.960
For example, if I tell you “Stand on your&nbsp;
heads, you will get to God”, you’ll do it.

00:20:48.960 --> 00:20:50.760
You’ll go on doing it.

00:20:50.760 --> 00:20:56.440
Till you’ll break your neck, land up in&nbsp;
the lunatic asylum you will go on doing it.&nbsp;

00:20:56.440 --> 00:21:03.120
But you must understand that how can&nbsp;
you achieve God by doing these things.&nbsp;

00:21:03.120 --> 00:21:05.640
These things anybody can do.

00:21:05.640 --> 00:21:10.120
All these things can be done by anyone whatsoever.

00:21:10.120 --> 00:21:14.880
But can you pulsate Kundalini&nbsp;
in the triangular bone?

00:21:14.880 --> 00:21:20.800
You cannot, that’s not possible for anyone.

00:21:20.800 --> 00:21:29.280
You can jump, you can shout, you can&nbsp;
scream, you can fly (She laughs), maybe,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:21:29.280 --> 00:21:36.000
I don’t know, but you cannot make your&nbsp;
Kundalini pulsate in the triangular bone.

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:38.040
Now it is for you to see.

00:21:38.040 --> 00:21:45.000
But if you are coming with this&nbsp;
doubting mind it just doesn’t work out.

00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:48.200
I’m not saying you should have faith in anyone,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:21:48.200 --> 00:21:52.400
blind faith is just the same,&nbsp;
another extreme of blind faith.

00:21:52.400 --> 00:21:55.760
They end up in lunatic asylum as I told you.

00:21:55.760 --> 00:21:57.720
The other day one gentleman met Me in India.

00:21:57.720 --> 00:22:03.840
He said that “My wife was a great Krishna Bhakta&nbsp;
and now she’s ended up in a lunatic asylum”.

00:22:03.840 --> 00:22:06.920
I said “What Krishna, which one?

00:22:06.920 --> 00:22:09.960
Was she connected with God?

00:22:09.960 --> 00:22:14.680
Did she know where Krishna resides within us?”.

00:22:14.680 --> 00:22:16.000
“No, she gave up the family.

00:22:16.000 --> 00:22:20.480
She said ‘I’ve become Meerabai’.”&nbsp;

00:22:20.480 --> 00:22:27.080
This is how we behave towards ourselves&nbsp;
when it comes to Sahaj Yog also.

00:22:27.080 --> 00:22:31.080
Now somebody asked Me today how&nbsp;
many, how much we have to meditate.

00:22:31.080 --> 00:22:32.680
I mean you don’t have to meditate at all,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:36.160
to be very frank.
I mean, I never meditate.

00:22:36.160 --> 00:22:37.760
I am in meditation all the time.

00:22:37.760 --> 00:22:40.040
I don’t know how to get out of it.

00:22:40.040 --> 00:22:42.560
(Laughter)
So you don’t meditate.

00:22:42.560 --> 00:22:47.600
You are in it!
But to be in it you have&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:22:47.600 --> 00:22:54.640
to practice a little bit, because you have been&nbsp;
identified with so many other things of life.

00:22:54.640 --> 00:23:00.000
Like, you can be easily thinking.

00:23:00.000 --> 00:23:06.320
I mean it’s easy for you to think, and&nbsp;
very difficult for you not to think,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:06.320 --> 00:23:08.680
because you have been doing like that.

00:23:08.680 --> 00:23:12.160
At the slightest pretext&nbsp;
you’ll jump into that thinking,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:23:12.160 --> 00:23:15.840
and once it starts the horse is galloping.

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:18.160
It doesn’t stop.

00:23:18.160 --> 00:23:23.200
So you have to learn to be&nbsp;
silent, to stop that thinking.

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:27.040
This is what you have to do.&nbsp;

00:23:27.040 --> 00:23:31.400
But in Sahaja Yoga also we&nbsp;
start thinking about it.

00:23:31.400 --> 00:23:35.740
What can you think about Sahaj Yog?

00:23:35.740 --> 00:23:41.600
Nothing! You leave it to thoughtless&nbsp;
awareness, in that state.

00:23:41.600 --> 00:23:47.720
So try to be in thoughtless&nbsp;
awareness as much as you can.

00:23:47.720 --> 00:23:54.000
But where do the Western Sahaja&nbsp;
Yogis fail – we must understand that.

00:23:54.000 --> 00:23:58.160
I’m sorry there are new people and I&nbsp;
shouldn’t expose many things about you.

00:23:58.160 --> 00:24:01.320
But doesn’t matter, they are our&nbsp;
children, they won’t feel bad about it.

00:24:01.320 --> 00:24:05.440
Where do we fail, we should face it.

00:24:05.440 --> 00:24:12.120
We feel this way, that so far&nbsp;
we have been great experts in&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:24:12.120 --> 00:24:16.680
spoiling everything, through our thinking.

00:24:16.680 --> 00:24:20.720
You give them a cake, they’ll&nbsp;
sit down and analyze it,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:24:20.720 --> 00:24:26.160
till that the cake will get all cold,&nbsp;
is finished, and you just can’t eat it.

00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:31.280
You give them a marriage – they’ll sit down&nbsp;
and analyze it, how to make yourself happy.

00:24:31.280 --> 00:24:34.920
I mean, you are happy there, why&nbsp;
do you have to think about it?

00:24:34.920 --> 00:24:37.160
So make a mess of your marriage.

00:24:37.160 --> 00:24:40.720
You give them children – you’ll sit down&nbsp;
and read some books about your children,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:24:40.720 --> 00:24:48.840
by the time the children will be&nbsp;
sick and would be good for nothing.

00:24:48.840 --> 00:24:52.040
So because of our rationality we have learnt to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:24:52.040 --> 00:24:56.760
make a mess of everything that&nbsp;
is living, that is joy-giving.

00:24:56.760 --> 00:25:02.320
We have closed our heart&nbsp;
completely with our rationality.

00:25:02.320 --> 00:25:08.720
So, to grow we should be a&nbsp;
little irrational in Sahaj Yoga.

00:25:08.720 --> 00:25:12.080
For example, if you are very meticulous,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:25:12.080 --> 00:25:18.320
very particular as you call it, you&nbsp;
must try to give up that extreme nature.

00:25:18.320 --> 00:25:23.440
But if you are extremely careless&nbsp;
or you don’t care for anything,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:25:23.440 --> 00:25:26.640
also that is extreme, that you have to give up.

00:25:26.640 --> 00:25:28.800
Both extremes are to be given up.

00:25:28.800 --> 00:25:32.800
You have to be in the center in your attitude.

00:25:32.800 --> 00:25:41.120
Then only you can grow because you know the sap&nbsp;
of life flows through your center, central channel&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:25:41.120 --> 00:25:51.720
of Sushumna, the parasympathetic, and that’s&nbsp;
why you should avoid all kinds of extremes.

00:25:51.720 --> 00:25:57.560
Even in Sahaja Yoga, one has to be careful.

00:25:57.560 --> 00:26:01.080
It is a mission, but it is&nbsp;
not a mission of missionaries.

00:26:01.080 --> 00:26:08.480
It is the mission of love as such, those&nbsp;
who love, those who love human beings.

00:26:08.480 --> 00:26:14.800
Nothing is more important than love in Sahaj Yoga.

00:26:14.800 --> 00:26:18.120
You can’t be harsh with people whom you love.

00:26:18.120 --> 00:26:23.200
If you love, if you say something to&nbsp;
them, doesn’t matter, they won’t feel bad.

00:26:23.200 --> 00:26:30.440
But if you don’t love and then just go on&nbsp;
sermoning and shouting at them, that’s no good.&nbsp;

00:26:30.440 --> 00:26:38.080
First establish your love&nbsp;
for yourself and for others.

00:26:38.080 --> 00:26:40.000
You have to establish your love.

00:26:40.000 --> 00:26:45.360
You should feel hankering for others.

00:26:45.360 --> 00:26:55.280
Now the competition has to change, the&nbsp;
style of competition among Sahaja Yogis,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:26:55.280 --> 00:26:58.240
the competition should be how much you love.

00:26:58.240 --> 00:27:01.360
Who loves more, let there be a competition.

00:27:01.360 --> 00:27:03.360
Who obliges you more.

00:27:03.360 --> 00:27:05.800
Who shares more.

00:27:05.800 --> 00:27:07.640
Who serves others more?

00:27:07.640 --> 00:27:15.400
Let there be a competition – in loving,&nbsp;
not in hating, not in finding faults,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:27:15.400 --> 00:27:19.760
in rationalizing I should say of everything.

00:27:19.760 --> 00:27:22.680
Love cannot be rationalized.

00:27:22.680 --> 00:27:27.000
I mean, people can’t understand&nbsp;
why I am so mad about you people.

00:27:27.000 --> 00:27:35.120
There’s so many people in India who are belonging&nbsp;
to the group to which my husband belongs,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:27:35.120 --> 00:27:38.200
that style – they can’t understand,&nbsp;
they said: “This woman has everything.

00:27:38.200 --> 00:27:40.560
Is She mad?

00:27:40.560 --> 00:27:45.640
She is going to the villages and wasting Her&nbsp;
life, why doesn’t She enjoy Herself?” See,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:27:45.640 --> 00:27:54.640
they can’t understand, I enjoy My love.
This is what you must know – to enjoy&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:27:54.640 --> 00:28:04.120
your virtues, and enjoy your love;&nbsp;
and you will be rewarded by it.

00:28:04.120 --> 00:28:06.720
It’s not hard, it’s the easiest thing.

00:28:06.720 --> 00:28:08.680
Supposing you love someone – supposing,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:14.560
I mean it’s a big supposition for many – but&nbsp;
supposing you really, genuinely love someone.

00:28:14.560 --> 00:28:20.000
Think like that, I mean in&nbsp;
imagination you can think of someone.&nbsp;

00:28:20.000 --> 00:28:28.320
Now that person is going to meet&nbsp;
you – say, you have to go to meet&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:28:28.320 --> 00:28:35.680
that person and there are lots&nbsp;
of odds, you cannot get a taxi,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:28:35.680 --> 00:28:40.080
you cannot get a train, you are worried:&nbsp;
“Now how to get to that person now.

00:28:40.080 --> 00:28:41.000
He would be waiting.

00:28:41.000 --> 00:28:43.920
And he would be worried or she would be waiting.

00:28:43.920 --> 00:28:45.520
Now what must be happening to them”.

00:28:45.520 --> 00:28:48.480
You are all the time thinking.

00:28:48.480 --> 00:28:50.960
And you are worried and then you don’t&nbsp;
know what to do, “Should we walk?”.

00:28:50.960 --> 00:28:55.560
Then you walk a little distance and you come&nbsp;
back, “No, might get a train, let’s try this”.

00:28:55.560 --> 00:28:58.800
You try all kinds of things, you&nbsp;
see, just to reach that person.

00:28:58.800 --> 00:29:07.080
And then it’s raining, and don’t have an umbrella.
You get completely drenched.

00:29:07.080 --> 00:29:16.400
Absolutely fagged out, tired but still – and the&nbsp;
moment you meet the person, you see the person,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:29:16.400 --> 00:29:23.440
all the worries and all the turmoils, all the&nbsp;
troubles and all the labor that you have put in,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:29:23.440 --> 00:29:28.040
vanishes into thin air and the&nbsp;
joy fills your life completely.

00:29:30.440 --> 00:29:38.160
How love is rewarding!

00:29:38.160 --> 00:29:44.400
So one must learn to love and not to rationalize.

00:29:44.400 --> 00:29:53.040
There is big scope in Sahaja Yoga to rationalize&nbsp;
because you become even a freer person.

00:29:53.040 --> 00:29:55.920
You really become free.

00:29:55.920 --> 00:29:58.440
I mean, after Sahaj Yoga&nbsp;
if you want to go to hell,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:29:58.440 --> 00:30:05.720
you can go faster than anybody else can,&nbsp;
because you really become a free bird.

00:30:05.720 --> 00:30:12.520
And if you want to go to&nbsp;
heaven you can do the same.

00:30:12.520 --> 00:30:19.480
So, one has to know that we have to&nbsp;
learn to compete in loving each other.

00:30:19.480 --> 00:30:22.400
We have some very beautiful Sahaj Yogis here,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:30:22.400 --> 00:30:28.280
very beautiful, and they have said sometimes&nbsp;
such beautiful things about others that I&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:30:28.280 --> 00:30:33.040
sometimes in My vacant mood think&nbsp;
of them and I feel very happy.

00:30:33.040 --> 00:30:39.471
It’s just like poetry, to say&nbsp;
something good about others.

00:30:39.471 --> 00:30:51.400
You see, sometimes I provoke and then somebody&nbsp;
says good words about others – I feel very happy.

00:30:51.400 --> 00:30:56.760
Without love we are not going&nbsp;
to solve any problem whatsoever.

00:30:56.760 --> 00:31:01.680
What’s the use of having, say,&nbsp;
even 10,000 people with vibrations&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:31:01.680 --> 00:31:05.760
flowing without any love among them?
I mean, I just can’t think of such a thing.

00:31:05.760 --> 00:31:09.000
Once you are Realized, you should feel love.

00:31:09.000 --> 00:31:10.640
But you must fathom it.

00:31:10.640 --> 00:31:16.760
Because of rational habits, because of this&nbsp;
misidentifications before, you cannot give it up.&nbsp;

00:31:16.760 --> 00:31:25.400
You see you are afraid, people are&nbsp;
even afraid to express their love.

00:31:25.400 --> 00:31:27.920
Somebody brought some sweets one day.

00:31:28.560 --> 00:31:32.760
I said, “For whom?” He said, “For Sahaj Yogis.”&nbsp;
So I said, “Why are you giving Me?” He said,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:31:32.760 --> 00:31:42.080
“Mother, if You give it would be better,&nbsp;
otherwise they may little bit doubt me.”

00:31:42.080 --> 00:31:52.160
Sometimes we want to love, we want to express,&nbsp;
but we are afraid that people will misunderstand.

00:31:52.160 --> 00:31:55.920
Imagine, where are we?

00:31:55.920 --> 00:32:02.280
What sort of human beings we have become&nbsp;
that we are afraid to express our love!&nbsp;

00:32:02.280 --> 00:32:12.733
Then the recipients also they do not&nbsp;
want to have any love, how can that be?

00:32:12.733 --> 00:32:14.640
Is impossible.

00:32:14.640 --> 00:32:20.080
Every human being wants to be loved.

00:32:20.080 --> 00:32:25.758
They will be afraid today, tomorrow,&nbsp;
day after they will be all right.

00:32:25.758 --> 00:32:28.080
[Shri Mataji is now talking about a child]
It’s a born realized child.

00:32:28.080 --> 00:32:31.920
See how, what a personality! It’s a born realized.

00:32:31.920 --> 00:32:35.520
So many children are born&nbsp;
realized, do you know that?

00:32:35.520 --> 00:32:40.480
Now, how many of you really&nbsp;
know about Realization?

00:32:40.480 --> 00:32:49.800
These great children are born to you and&nbsp;
you don’t know anything about Realization.&nbsp;

00:32:49.800 --> 00:32:58.120
So, we have to be bold about&nbsp;
our love and little shameless.

00:32:58.120 --> 00:33:03.240
Let people feel bad, let them think&nbsp;
wrong about us, doesn’t matter.

00:33:03.240 --> 00:33:06.800
But express your love.

00:33:06.800 --> 00:33:10.240
But it should not be filthy love.

00:33:10.240 --> 00:33:11.800
It should not be mixed love.

00:33:11.800 --> 00:33:17.120
It should not be with some&nbsp;
sort of a possessiveness in it.

00:33:17.120 --> 00:33:20.520
It should not be love in which&nbsp;
you are expressing something else.

00:33:20.520 --> 00:33:27.760
It should be pure love as the name of your&nbsp;
Mother is, absolutely emitting from you.

00:33:29.040 --> 00:33:38.640
Not with any idea, with any game, with anything&nbsp;
whatsoever, because you should know that there&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:51.440
is something very beautiful hidden within everyone&nbsp;
of you, which your Mother can see – and She loves,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:33:51.440 --> 00:33:56.640
loves that part that is within you&nbsp;
which is about to be born again.

00:33:56.640 --> 00:34:01.480
And you are that beautiful.

00:34:01.480 --> 00:34:08.720
In the same way you should love all the Sahaja&nbsp;
Yogis and all the other people of this world,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:34:08.720 --> 00:34:18.120
because they are all beautiful&nbsp;
beings just covered with three gunas.

00:34:18.120 --> 00:34:27.720
Let them be that and then your&nbsp;
Spirit will recognize the joy.

00:34:29.960 --> 00:34:31.920
Will emit the joy.

00:34:31.920 --> 00:34:37.080
You will be a source of joy and&nbsp;
you will give joy to others.

00:34:37.080 --> 00:34:43.160
Give up all your wrong ideas and your set ideas&nbsp;
about things, absolutely they are all wrong.

00:34:43.160 --> 00:34:48.160
Like Hitler believing that all Jews killed Christ.

00:34:48.160 --> 00:34:57.760
It was he who killed Christ and he was&nbsp;
killing all the Jews because Christ was a Jew.

00:34:57.760 --> 00:35:04.320
He thought killing one Jew was not&nbsp;
sufficient so kill all the rest of them.&nbsp;

00:35:04.320 --> 00:35:08.240
All those who hate have reasoning behind it.

00:35:08.240 --> 00:35:11.920
They have to give some reasoning because&nbsp;
they cannot hate without reasoning.

00:35:11.920 --> 00:35:14.240
Those who love do not need any reasoning.

00:35:14.240 --> 00:35:15.840
They have no time to reason it out.

00:35:15.840 --> 00:35:19.240
They just love.

00:35:19.240 --> 00:35:27.760
Because they can see something;&nbsp;
that love gives them that sight&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:35:27.760 --> 00:35:34.160
of the beauty of others which is hidden in them.
Sometimes some people can be very arrogant,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:35:34.160 --> 00:35:39.920
you have seen how people have been rude to Me:&nbsp;
makes no difference to Me, to be very frank,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:35:39.920 --> 00:35:50.840
because I know behind this rudeness lies that&nbsp;
thinking, so respect, respect each other.

00:35:50.840 --> 00:35:57.200
And know that you have that joy, and you&nbsp;
have that power to give that joy to others;&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:35:57.200 --> 00:36:02.080
and when you give that joy, that&nbsp;
joy returns back to you as joy.

00:36:02.080 --> 00:36:06.720
So what lacks in us that we&nbsp;
do not give joy to others.

00:36:06.720 --> 00:36:14.560
Unless and until you give joy to others&nbsp;
the joy doesn’t return back to you.

00:36:14.560 --> 00:36:17.040
That’s the lacking.&nbsp;

00:36:17.040 --> 00:36:22.840
Now do not rationalize that either.
Immediately people start thinking about it.

00:36:22.840 --> 00:36:26.940
We have done a lot, I can tell you, we&nbsp;
are enjoying each other quite a lot.

00:36:26.940 --> 00:36:28.560
It’s really enjoyable.

00:36:28.560 --> 00:36:34.520
If it was not so, you would not have been&nbsp;
there together, because there is nothing&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:36:34.520 --> 00:36:42.280
binding otherwise between us, except for&nbsp;
love, except for that joy-giving love.

00:36:42.280 --> 00:36:47.160
There’s nothing else, because&nbsp;
we have no money transactions,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:36:47.160 --> 00:36:50.440
there’s no business on here at all, any kind.

00:36:50.440 --> 00:36:57.520
There is no intellectual rapport&nbsp;
going on between you and Me,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:36:58.600 --> 00:37:05.680
neither there is possibility of Me getting&nbsp;
elected to the parliament (laughter), nor&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:37:05.680 --> 00:37:16.080
I belong to any leadership of any,&nbsp;
you can say, these striking people.&nbsp;

00:37:16.080 --> 00:37:20.040
Without all these things how&nbsp;
are we attached to each other?

00:37:20.040 --> 00:37:26.520
Because there’s something supreme that&nbsp;
we can get out of our relationships.

00:37:26.520 --> 00:37:37.493
That’s pure joy.
May God bless you all!

00:37:37.493 --> 00:37:37.800
[Shri Mataji is addressing a new person]

00:37:37.800 --> 00:37:40.440
…first time, is it?

00:37:40.440 --> 00:37:41.160
Good.&nbsp;

00:37:41.160 --> 00:37:47.080
Please put your, just your hands&nbsp;
like this, just straight like that.

00:37:47.080 --> 00:37:55.600
Both the feet should be touching the Mother&nbsp;
Earth, just like… with love; just touch you.

00:37:55.600 --> 00:38:02.840
Just put your hands like this, straight.

00:38:02.840 --> 00:38:10.000
You may close your eyes, yes,&nbsp;
close your eyes, just close.

00:38:10.000 --> 00:38:18.680
Please close your eyes, close&nbsp;
your eyes, close your eyes.

00:38:18.680 --> 00:38:20.680
Keep your feet steady.

00:38:20.680 --> 00:38:22.920
Steady, steady yourself.

00:38:22.920 --> 00:38:27.440
Just steady yourself, and relaxed, relax.

00:38:29.840 --> 00:38:37.720
Put your hands on your lap,&nbsp;
if you think it’s strenuous.

00:38:37.720 --> 00:38:40.200
Got it.

00:38:40.200 --> 00:38:41.000
Yes.

00:38:41.000 --> 00:38:53.720
Just enjoy yourself, you have got it.

00:38:53.720 --> 00:38:57.440
All you will start feeling cool&nbsp;
breeze in your hand, most of you.

00:39:04.320 --> 00:39:13.240
It’s a tremendous experience, try to remember it.

00:39:13.240 --> 00:39:16.640
If you can put your bag down, down will be better.

00:39:16.640 --> 00:39:20.400
And are you wearing a coat also?

00:39:20.400 --> 00:39:21.280
Is she wearing a coat?

00:39:21.280 --> 00:39:26.240
She has to be little comfortable.
Yes.

00:39:26.240 --> 00:39:28.440
And – are you wearing a coat?

00:39:28.440 --> 00:39:34.200
Think if you take out your coat&nbsp;
would be better, yes, be comfortable.

00:39:38.600 --> 00:39:42.800
Yes.

00:39:43.600 --> 00:39:46.764
Yes.

00:39:46.764 --> 00:39:46.774
Yes, yes.

00:39:46.774 --> 00:39:49.538
What’s the matter?
Lady: I had an open heart operation.

00:39:49.538 --> 00:39:50.520
Shri Mataji: Eh?
Lady: I had an open&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:39:50.520 --> 00:39:54.280
heart operation and I still can’t walk, you know.

00:39:54.280 --> 00:39:55.760
These are shoes.

00:39:55.760 --> 00:39:56.390
Shri Mataji: Alright.

00:39:56.390 --> 00:40:00.300
They’ll bring your shoes, please.
Lady: I have… – I have in my bag.&nbsp;

00:40:00.300 --> 00:40:01.960
Shri Mataji: Alright, let her wear the shoes.

00:40:01.960 --> 00:40:02.480
Lady: Yes?

00:40:02.480 --> 00:40:10.320
Thank you.
Shri Mataji: Yes, please.

00:40:10.320 --> 00:40:10.640
It’s now, you – I’ll see afterwards&nbsp;
little bit, I’ll just treat you, so later&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:40:10.640 --> 00:40:11.800
on you can get it, alright?

00:40:11.800 --> 00:40:20.427
I will just treat you.
Lady:… my bag…&nbsp;

00:40:20.427 --> 00:40:21.840
Shri Mataji: Keep them down there, keep&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:40:21.840 --> 00:40:24.572
the shoes down, just relax.
Lady: Thank you.

00:40:24.572 --> 00:40:25.160
I’m so sorry.
Shri Mataji: Can you remove&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:40:25.160 --> 00:40:26.640
this from here – don’t be sorry.

00:40:26.640 --> 00:40:27.620
Just enjoy.

00:40:27.620 --> 00:40:28.840
Please sit down comfortably.

00:40:28.840 --> 00:40:32.480
Be comfortably, it’s alright.

00:40:32.480 --> 00:40:38.320
It’s My job.&nbsp;

00:40:39.480 --> 00:40:48.800
You got it! (She laughs) You have got it too!
